    "Data frequency matters to Bitcoin investors as its properties vary across time horizons (Bouri et al. 2017a).",
    "It acts as a strong hedge and safe haven against fluctuations in commodity market indices (Bouri et al. 2017b).",
    "However, Klein et al. (2018) find no hedging ability against a decline in equity prices, and it can hedge against uncertainties (Bouri et al. 2017c).",
